<item>
            <title>[LU-16612] cl_page_state_set0() LBUG</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16612</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Got 2 cases about cl_page_state_set0()) LBUG.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;(cl_page_state_set0()) allowed_transitions&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;old&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;state&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
cl_page_state_set0+0x504/0x8f0 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
cl_page_assume+0x130/0x4a0 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
ll_read_ahead_page+0x5cc/0x730 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;lustre&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;And the cl_page cp_state is 2 (CPS_PAGEOUT) cp_owner has value. The page is meant to transit from CACHED to OWNED, but it already has been in PAGEOUT state.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;(cl_page.c:346:cl_page_state_set0()) equi(state == CPS_OWNED, page-&amp;gt;cp_owner != NULL)&lt;br/&gt;
 cl_page_state_set0+0x3ef/0x3f0 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 cl_page_io_start+0x46/0x110 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 cl_page_prep+0x170/0x190 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obdclass&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 osc_io_submit+0x1e8/0x730 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;osc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;And the cl_page cp_state is 1 (CPS_OWNED) cp_onwer has value. The page is meant to transit from OWNED to PAGEOUT, but cl_page_io_start() should has cleared its cp_owner.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
